rows.label: tlk70000043_03_msg0001
rows.name:
I've only been in Iira a
short time and I find myself
with many new contacts.

rows.label: tlk70000043_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Lots of them pester me as
an Superbian chef to make
them Superbian food...

rows.label: tlk70000043_03_msg0003
rows.name: But I've not got the guts fer that!!!

rows.label: tlk70000043_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Iirans just don't realise how
luxurious their tastes are. How
refined their palates are!

rows.label: tlk70000043_03_msg0005
rows.name:
Being used to such delicate flavors and
rich tastes, I know exactly how they'll
react to authentic Superbian food.

rows.label: tlk70000043_03_msg0006
rows.name:
Once they've got the idea that
"Superbian food is disgusting" in
their heads, they'll never eat it again.

rows.label: tlk70000043_03_msg0007
rows.name:
That's pretty hard for me. As a
cook, and as an Superbian...

rows.label: tlk70000043_03_msg0008
rows.name:
That's why it's essential for me
to study Iiran cuisine. To start a
revolution in Superbian cooking!
